---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="5 Common Website Mistakes Costing Local Businesses Customers | Shelby Web Company"
  description="Is your website driving customers away? Discover the 5 most common website mistakes for local businesses and how to fix them."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-accent/20 bg-brand-accent/5">
          <span class="text-brand-accent text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Web Design</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #1 Article #3 • January 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          5 Common Website Mistakes <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Costing You Customers</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
          And How to Fix Them Before It's Too Late
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12 px-4">Common Website <br/> Pitfalls</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          Your website is often the first impression a potential customer has of your business. But what happens when that first impression is a bad one? Every day, local businesses lose customers—not because of poor service or high prices—but because of easily fixable website mistakes.
        </p>

        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          After working with dozens of local businesses in Shelby and Cleveland County, we've identified the five most common website problems that drive customers away—and the good news is, every single one of them can be fixed.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> Slow Loading Speeds
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-6">
          In 2026, patience is in short supply. Studies show that <strong>53% of mobile users abandon a site that takes longer than 3 seconds to load.</strong> If your website is sluggish, customers aren't waiting—they're clicking over to your competitor.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 border-l-4 border-brand-cyan p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl">
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">The Fix:</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 m-0">Optimize images, use modern hosting, and eliminate bloated code. A fast website isn't a luxury—it's a necessity.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> Missing Contact Information
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-6">
          You'd be surprised how many websites make it nearly impossible to find a phone number or email address. If a customer has to hunt for your contact info, they'll give up and call someone else.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 border-l-4 border-brand-cyan p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl">
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">The Fix:</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 m-0">Put your phone number and email in the header. Add a clear "Contact Us" button that's visible on every page.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">03.</span> Not Mobile-Responsive
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-6">
          Over 60% of web traffic now comes from mobile devices. If your website looks broken, cramped, or impossible to navigate on a phone, you're losing the majority of your potential customers before they even see what you offer.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 border-l-4 border-brand-cyan p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl">
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">The Fix:</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 m-0">Your website must look and function beautifully on screens of all sizes. Period.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">04.</span> Ignoring Local SEO
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-6">
          If your website doesn't mention your city, service areas, or local keywords, Google doesn't know where to show your business. And if you haven't claimed or optimized your Google Business Profile, you're invisible on Maps.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 border-l-4 border-brand-cyan p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl">
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">The Fix:</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 m-0">Add location-specific content, claim your Google Business Profile, and build local citations. Show up where your customers are searching.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">05.</span> Outdated Design
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-6">
          Design trends evolve, and customers notice. An outdated website with clunky layouts, tiny fonts, or early-2000s clip art signals that your business might be behind the times—even if your services are top-notch.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 border-l-4 border-brand-cyan p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl">
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">The Fix:</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 m-0">A modern, clean design builds trust instantly. It tells customers you care about quality in everything you do.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/10 to-transparent border border-brand-blue/20 p-8 my-16 rounded-3xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">Quick Website Checklist</h3>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90">Loads in &lt; 3 seconds</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90">Phone/email on all pages</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90">Perfect on mobile</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90">GBP profile claimed</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8">The Bottom Line</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-12">
            These mistakes aren't just inconveniences—they're actively costing you money. Every slow page load, every hidden phone number, every pinch-to-zoom moment on mobile is a customer walking out the door.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-darkest p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(0,255,255,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10 text-center">FREE Website Audit</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Not sure if your website is making these mistakes? Let us take a look—no strings attached.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-brand-darkest px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-sky transition-all">
              Request Your Audit
            </a>
            <a href="/services/web-design" class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-black/30 transition-all">
              View Design Services
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 p-8 bg-brand-dark/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl text-center">
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm mb-4">
                This article was written and published by <strong>Shelby Web Company</strong> to help local businesses thrive in the digital age.
            </p>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm m-0">
                Ready to level up your online presence? Visit <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline">www.shelbywebco.com</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">About Us</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
